<topic id='business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Non-Consultant Led Activity - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 where a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>
 does not retain overall clinical responsibility for 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 care.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_main_specialty">MAIN SPECIALTY</xref>
 will be recorded using the appropriate default 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_main_specialty_code">MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
 for the type of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 along with a default 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_consultant_code">CONSULTANT CODE</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_main_specialty_code">MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
 is used by the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/secondary_uses_service.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Secondary_Uses_Service</xref>
 to identify 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
.  </p>

